</ul>



<p>Understanding the impact of staking on ADA distribution is essential for individuals looking to leverage Cardano ADA&#8217;s utility and explore its investment potential. It also allows traders to develop effective trading strategies based on the dynamics of staking and the overall economic model of Cardano ADA.</p>



